SessionCompacted()` â€” Logging only (like `handleGeminiPreCompress`)\n\n**Reusable functions** (no duplication):\n- `handleSessionStartCommon()` from `hooks.go:242` â€” shared session start logic\n- `CapturePrePromptState()` from `state.go:67` â€” captures untracked files + JSONL line count\n- `ComputeFileChanges()` from `state.go` â€” git status for new/deleted files\n- `FilterAndNormalizePaths()` â€” path normalization\n- `generateCommitMessage()` â€” commit message from prompt\n- `GetGitAuthor()` â€” git author info\n- `transitionSessionTurnEnd()` â€” session phase transition\n- `outputHookResponse()` â€” JSON response output\n- `markSessionEnded()` â€” marks session as ENDED\n- `copyFile()` â€” file copy utility\n\n### Step 4: Register Handlers\n\n**Modify:** `cmd/entire/cli/hook_registry.go`\n\nAdd import: `\"github.com/entireio/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/openclaw\"`\n\nRegister 5 handlers in `init()`:\n- `(AgentNameOpenClaw, HookNameBootstrap)` â†’ `handleOpenClawBootstrap()`\n- `(AgentNameOpenClaw, HookNameResponse)` â†’ `handleOpenClawResponse()`\n- `(AgentNameOpenClaw, HookNameCommandNew)` â†’ `handleOpenClawCommandNew()`\n- `(AgentNameOpenClaw, HookNameCommandStop)` â†’ `handleOpenClawCommandStop()`\n- `(AgentNameOpenClaw, HookNameSessionCompacted)` â†’ `handleOpenClawSessionCompacted()`\n\nEach wrapped with `IsEnabled()` check.\n\n### Step 5: Add Blank Import\n\n**Modify:** `cmd/entire/cli/hooks_cmd.go`\n\n```go\n_ \"github.com/entireio/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/openclaw\"\n```\n\n### Step 6: Tests\n\n**New files:**\n\n- `cmd/entire/cli/agent/openclaw/openclaw_test.go` â€” Agent interface tests (ParseHookInput variants, DetectPresence, GetSessionDir, ReadSession, WriteSession, FormatResumeCommand, TranscriptPosition, ChunkTranscript)\n- `cmd/entire/cli/agent/openclaw/hooks_test.go` â€” Hook management tests (InstallHooks fresh/idempotent/force/localDev, UninstallHooks, AreHooksInstalled, GetHookNames)\n- `cmd/entire/cli/agent/openclaw/transcript_test.go` â€